<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DSHI 대시보드 로그인</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .login-container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
        }
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .logo p {
            color: #666;
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .form-group input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .form-group input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #667eea;
        }
        .btn-login {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-login:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        .error {
            background: #fee;
            color: #c33;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #fcc;
        }
        .info {
            background: #f0f8ff;
            color: #0066cc;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            border: 1px solid #cce6ff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="logo">
            <h1>DSHI 대시보드</h1>
            <p>조립품 진행 현황 관리</p>
        </div>
        
        <% if @error %>
            <div class="error">
                <%= @error %>
            </div>
        <% end %>
        
        <form method="POST" action="/login">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="username">사용자명</label>
                <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required autofocus>
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="password">비밀번호</label>
                <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>
            </div>
            
            <button type="submit" class="btn-login">로그인</button>
        </form>
        
        <div class="info">
            <strong>접근 권한:</strong> Level 3 이상의 관리자만 접근 가능합니다.<br>
            <strong>개발용 계정:</strong> admin / dshi2024
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>